      "content": "Also I want to highlight that when you VOD review you MUST write down the mistakes you made etc and how you will improve them and actually TAKE ACTION. I see too many people \"fake VOD\" reviewing and saying they’re a grinder — they’re not, they’re just wasting their own time thinking they’re productive. How can you improve if you will not even improve and take action on your mistakes to not make them again?\n\nLastly stop blaming your teammates and having a new teammate every week, maybe it’s you who needs to improve (harsh reality guys but sometimes you need to be tough on yourself to succeed).\n\nIf you want a training routine you can use https://discord.com/channels/971731167621574666/1426073254585696298/1467715808103759964",
